## 🚀 Deployment

<!-- {{#if tauri}} -->
**Desktop App Distribution**:
```bash
# Build production app
{{packageManager}} run tauri build

# Generates platform-specific installers:
# - macOS: .dmg, .app
# - Windows: .msi, .exe
# - Linux: .deb, .AppImage
```
<!-- {{/if}} -->

<!-- {{#if nextjs-aws}} -->
**Web App Deployment**:
```bash
# Deploy to AWS
cd infrastructure
cdk deploy

# Deploys to:
# - Frontend: S3 + CloudFront
# - Backend: Lambda + API Gateway
# - Database: RDS/DynamoDB
```
<!-- {{/if}} -->

<!-- {{#if tauri-aws}} -->
**Hybrid Deployment**:
1. **Desktop App**: Build installers for distribution
2. **Cloud Backend**: Deploy to AWS with CDK
```bash
# Build desktop app
{{packageManager}} run tauri build

# Deploy backend
cd infrastructure
cdk deploy
```
<!-- {{/if}} -->

See [Deployment Guide](DEPLOYMENT.md) for detailed procedures.

